    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You\u2019ve seriously gotta see this beauty! I\u2019ve taken incredible care of this car, and it\u2019s honestly in show-quality condition\u2014totally spotless inside and out. It\u2019s been garage-kept, meticulously maintained, and still drives like it just rolled off the lot. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been truly loved and looks absolutely pristine, this is the one for you! I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have. Come take a peek and fall in love!",
