    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an exceptional 2002 BMW M3 (E46) in collector-grade condition. This example is powered by the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and double VANOS, delivering a linear power band up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory limited-slip differential. Meticulous preventative maintenance includes documented rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive rear subframe reinforcement. The chassis remains taut with upgraded bushings and Bilstein dampers, while the exterior retains its factory finish with consistent paint depth readings across all panels. This is a mechanically turn-key specimen with zero deferred maintenance, ideal for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
