    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is an absolute time capsule, preserved in a climate-controlled garage and maintained with meticulous attention to detail. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with a professionally applied ceramic coating; the body is entirely free of stone chips, door dings, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin retains its original factory-fresh scent, with premium leather surfaces that show no signs of creasing and electronics that function flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, accompanied by a comprehensive service binder documenting every scheduled maintenance and fluid flush. The engine bay is detailed to showroom standards, and the sale includes all original keys, manuals, and window stickers. This is a museum-quality example intended for a collector who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
