    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle remains in concours-level condition, exhibiting a flawless exterior finish and an interior that retains its original showroom integrity. Every mechanical component has been fastidiously maintained to ensure peak performance. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than excellence, this offering represents a rare opportunity to acquire a truly immaculate example of engineering and design.",
      "price": 48500.0,
