    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014it honestly looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I've babied it since day one, keeping it spotless and staying on top of every single service. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s practically perfect and ready for its next adventure, you\u2019ve found it! Feel free to reach out if you want to take a look!",
      "price": 46500.0,
