    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. The S54 power plant remains factory-tight, delivering linear power through its six individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double VANOS system. Power is transferred via a precise Getrag 6-speed manual to a variable M-differential lock, ensuring optimal mechanical grip. The chassis exhibits zero fatigue, with all bushings and suspension components maintained to a forensic standard. Finished in a flawless coat with an interior devoid of bolster wear or UV degradation, this example offers a visceral, analog driving experience that is increasingly rare.",
